Instruction: As an expert in code conversion, your task is to convert the provided Jinja template to its equivalent Blended template. Blended is a variant of Jinja with strict type checking and scoping rules.

### Task Description:
45. print the string "Process completed" and then render it after converting to lowercase

### Jinja Template:
{{ "Process completed" }}
{{ "Process completed" | lower }}

### Blended Template:
{% print "Process completed" }
{{ lower("Process completed") }}
